  <compounddef id="generate__reference_8py" kind="file" language="Python">
    <compoundname>generate_reference.py</compoundname>
    <innernamespace refid="namespacegenerate__reference">generate_reference</innernamespace>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Generates ground-truth makespans and operation schedules from job_shop_lib for cross-validation against the C# DES simulator. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Runs every rule in RULES against every instance in INSTANCES using job_shop_lib&apos;s <computeroutput>DispatchingRuleSolver</computeroutput>, then writes two output files whose structure is kept deliberately in sync with the C# <computeroutput>ValidationExporter</computeroutput> outputs:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>reference_makespans.csv</computeroutput> — one row per instance/rule combination, with columns matching <computeroutput>csharp_makespans.csv</computeroutput> for direct DataFrame merging in <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>reference_schedules.json</computeroutput> — full operation-level schedule per instance/rule, keyed as <computeroutput>&quot;{instance}_{rule_key}&quot;</computeroutput>, for divergence analysis in <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput> and <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__mirror_8py" kindref="compound">compare_mirror.py</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Prerequisites</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>job-shop-lib<sp/>pandas</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">python<sp/>generate_reference.py</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="par"><title>Output</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>reference_makespans.csv</computeroutput> — ground-truth makespans for all instance/rule pairs.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>reference_schedules.json</computeroutput> — per-instance/rule operation lists sorted by start time, then machine ID, then job ID.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>A pivot table printed to stdout summarising makespan by instance × rule.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>The C# simulator should produce identical makespans for all mapped rules. If not, the schedule JSON lets <computeroutput><ref refid="compare__results_8py" kindref="compound">compare_results.py</ref></computeroutput> identify exactly which operation first diverges between the two implementations. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
